Overview:
• Bored at work? In line at the supermarket? Need to keep the kids entertained? Android has a hidden video game.

◆Steps:
● Go to Settings > System > About Phone (or Software info),
● Click on “Android version,” tap on it multiple times and you’ll
    see a logo for Nougat or Marshmallow.
● Tap a few times again and now press and hold the circle on
    the screen. A secret minigame will appear.
● Trt this small sized too much hard game.
